Yeah. Getting old... it sucks.

157
00:07:45,115 --> 00:07:46,593
Guess it's better
than the alternative.

158
00:07:46,617 --> 00:07:48,033
Let me see that.

159
00:07:51,821 --> 00:07:53,088
Your feet swollen, too?

160
