unofficial historian.

218
00:09:59,583 --> 00:10:01,649
Keeper of secrets.

219
00:10:01,685 --> 00:10:03,768
Oh, I've seen a few things.

220
00:10:03,804 --> 00:10:05,831
I was here when
Randolph was a resident.

221
