All right, spit it out, boys.

234
00:10:50,384 --> 00:10:53,217
That's not supposed
to be on my heart, is it?

235
00:10:53,253 --> 00:10:54,947
No.

236
00:10:54,971 --> 00:10:56,337
It's called a myxoma.

237
00:10:56,372 --> 00:10:58,673
It's probably been
growing there for months.

238
00:10:58,725 --> 00:11:00,991
Thing got so big
it started to block

239
00:11:01,028 --> 00:11:02,738
- the blood flow to your heart.
- Which explains

240
00:11:02,762 --> 00:11:04,457
the fluid buildup
and pitting edema.

241
