242
00:11:06,266 --> 00:11:08,116
Look, the good news is

243
00:11:08,151 --> 00:11:11,018
we caught it early
while it's still operable.

244
00:11:11,071 --> 00:11:13,032
When Bell brought
you in for testing...

245
00:11:13,056 --> 00:11:14,705
he probably saved your life.

246
00:11:16,159 --> 00:11:18,960
Well... I guess
being friends with you

